message: Bob, I've proposed to divide the $10,000 with me receiving $6,000 and you receiving $4,000. I believe this is a fair offer that benefits us both. Let me know if you accept or if you want to propose something different!
Lota, I appreciate your offer but I believe we can both get a better deal. I propose we split it 60/40 in my favor. This reflects the value I bring to the table.  Let's get this done.
